name: Sunjoy Grill Gazebo with Built-in Hooks and Polyester Canopy
description: Shade yourself and your grill with this handsome fabric-top grill gazebo. The gazebo features convenient built-in hooks to hang grill tools within an arms reach or plants to spruce up your grilling area. This grill gazebo sets up in minutes, taking the chore out of installation. Convenience and value all rolled up into one pretty package.Protects you and your grill from sun, rain and debrisLightweight, easy to move or repositionEasy to clean polyester canopyBuilt from durable steel
